Citing Blosc
============

You can cite our work on the various libraries under the Blosc umbrella as follows:

.. code-block:: console

  @ONLINE{blosc,
    author = {{Blosc Development Team}},
    title = "{A fast, compressed and persistent data store library}",
    year = {2009-2026},
    note = {https://blosc.org}
  }

